<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>أَقْسَامُ الدِّيَةِ بِاعْتِبَارِ مَنْ تَجِبُ عَلَيْه<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>الدِّيَةُ عَلَى الْعَاقِلَة<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(جة)</span> , وَعَنْ الْمُغِيرَةِ بْنِ شُعْبَةَ - رضي الله عنه -<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c1">" قَضَى رَسُولُ اللهِ - صلى الله عليه وسلم - بِالدِّيَةِ عَلَى الْعَاقِلَةِ "</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) (جة) ٢٦٣٣ , (خ) ٦٥١٢ , (م) ٣٨ - (١٦٨٢)</p> </div>